<i>adjective</i>: 광범하다 [광ː범하다], 광범위하다 [광ː버뮈하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>광범하다 [광ː범하다]</dt><br>
<dd>extensive; widespread; far-reaching</dd><br>
<dd>범위가 넓다.</dd><br>
<dd>A range being wide.</dd><br>
